  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      It is a cross-sectional study to summarize the extracorporeal membrane oxygenation&#xD;
      （ECMO）treatment in children in China.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      ECMO treatment in children is still in its infancy in China, and it has made considerable&#xD;
      progress in recent years. In order to further understand the development of ECMO treatment in&#xD;
      critically ill children, the investigator conduct this cross-sectional research through&#xD;
      questionnaires. The investigator collect general information of the hospital and ECMO&#xD;
      equipment, etiology, compilation, and mode of ECMO.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
